elements.title: Productos TotalBeauty 2017
elements.description: When it comes to battling blemishes, three major ingredients seem to get all the love: salicylic acid, benzoyl peroxide, and retinoids. And while we'd never knock this top trio (they are proven to be supereffective, after all), sometimes you need a gentler, more natural way to clear your complexion

elements.title: Valia Skincare
elements.description: VALIA Purifying Wash is made of an effective blend of plant-based ingredients, herbal extracts and essential oils such as Green Tea, Vitamin C and Yuzu to encourage cell turnover for a brighter, more radiant complexion. It is perfect for people looking for a light cleanser that naturally hydrates and moisturizes.

elements.title: Jules Esther Skincare
elements.description: Regenerate, brighten, and smooth skin with this anti-aging powerhouse packed with Omegas 3, 6, 7, and 9

elements.title: Concurso Ossira invierno 2017
elements.description: La tendencia la inauguró Kendall Jenner y enseguida se sumaron otras Insta-girls y supermodelos, entre ellas la brasileña Sara Sampaio. Se puede llevar a la vista, con una camisa abierta, por debajo de un top transparente o con una pieza-top de lencería por encima de una camiseta blanca.
